title: Adding "defaultprevalence"
body:
I have modified ENMevaluate.R and make.args.R in order to be able to modify the parameter "prevalence" to be passed to maxent.
The default value is still 0.5, but it can be modified, if necessary, when you call the function ENMevaluate.
I would very much appreciate any comment you can do to this modification.
Thanks.
Xavier Rotllan-Puig
